# dexora-landing project intelligence

Marketing site for Dexora at **https://www.dexora.app**.

- **Repo:** https://github.com/semprog25/dexora-landing
- **Companion app repo:** https://github.com/semprog25/Dexora (Dexora-main)

## Legal pages (Play Store / App Store)

| Page | URL |
| --- | --- |
| Privacy | https://www.dexora.app/privacy |
| Delete account | https://www.dexora.app/delete-account |
| Terms | https://www.dexora.app/terms |

Source of truth: `src/lib/legal-content.ts` — static copies generated at build time via `scripts/generate-legal-pages.mjs`.

## Deploy

Push to `main` → GitHub Actions deploys `dist/` to `gh-pages` branch → served at www.dexora.app.
